                    <p>Professional repair services and premium hardware solutions. We specialize in fixing agricultural machinery and providing quality tools for your needs.</p>
                </section>
                
                <section id='services' style='padding: 2rem 0;'>
                    <h2 style='text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; font-weight: 800;'>Our Services</h2>
