                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style='text-align: center; margin-top: 4rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);'>
                <p style='color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem;'>&#169; 2024 Antinna.in. All rights reserved.</p>
